KitKat::

She followed Carnatron and assisted Desctuctor as he needed. Her 
wounds were sever, leaving a trail of mech fluid as she walked. Her 
life support meter showed she had 20% left. Yet, she held her head up 
high and tried her best not to show the pain that was surging through 
her body. Her optics started to flicker as the evergon level started 
to drop.  She was not going to give in to the pain, but the pain was 
increasing.
